column8: Sunny morning. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and early evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds westerly 20 to 25 km/h becoming light in the early afternoon.
Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower in the morning. Light winds becoming northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the middle of the day.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning and afternoon. Winds north to northwesterly 30 to 45 km/h turning westerly 25 to 30 km/h during the evening.
Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. Winds west to northwesterly 25 to 30 km/h turning northerly 20 to 25 km/h during the morning then increasing to 30 to 35 km/h during the evening.
Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of showers. Winds northerly 30 to 35 km/h tending northwesterly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. Winds northwest to southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h tending east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h.
